&lt;h1 id=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;heading&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Simple paragraph.
Spread across two lines in markdown.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;block&quot;&gt;block&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Special &lt;code&gt;text&lt;/code&gt;. Sometimes &lt;em&gt;important&lt;/em&gt;. Sometimes &lt;strong&gt;big&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This should show up as a quote
in block form.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
